   Call ECR_TRACE([F:AOT]TABACT-":"-[F:AOB]ABREV-mess(56,123,1)-[F:AOT]TABFIC,0) From GESECRAN : # Table
  Endif
 Next AOT
Next
Close Local File [AOB] , [AOT]
Call ECR_TRACE("",0) From GESECRAN
